- user can signup
- user credentials are stored in database
- user can login
- system will authenticate the user and take them to an empty page for now.

===========================================================================

- the email of the user will be registered to the domain '@mufa'
- the user can transition from signup -> login page and vice versa
- Sign Up Page:
	- Email input field
	- Password input field
	- Button (signup)
	- Button (Already have an account? login)

- Login Page:
	- Email input field
	- Password input field
	- Button (Login)
	- Button (Don't have an account? Signup)
